track_notes:
Very nice place to be! The walk is a bit long but you will disurb all the goats around the summit! be carefull at the summit, the hole in your back is very deep. Enought place for a dipole. Easy parking on the road
Quite long and difficult if you are not fit and healthy, the place is splendid and must be done in summer when wx is fine, take some water and hat of course; you can park easyly at the stat point.
